/*                  by GLC008142 which was made redundant).          */
/*       MD039002 - U1 must be on to allow closure of accounts       */
/*                  Apply CC2903 that was done in GLCP018.           */
/*       MD037383 - ACCNTAB blank after COB component GLC008140 00001*/
